title: One-Bedroom Apartment with a Full Suite of Efficient GE Appliances
posting_body: Whether you want to plant roots or branch out, Parallel Garden is your sanctuary in Sunnyvale.
Join us for a self-guided or virtual tour!
Explore your new home from the comfort of your couch, or on a self-guided journey through our Neighborhood.
Tucked along a tree-lined lane, Parallel Apartments in Sunnyvale is a relaxing refuge.
Step away from the Silicon Valley hustle, and indulge in a one-bedroom that’s big on space and privacy.
Enjoy the quiet with your own private patio with high fencing, a perfect retreat after a long day.
Oversized closets and open floor plans make it easy to settle in and take root.
You can be more in the moment knowing there’s no one above or below you with no upstairs or downstairs neighbors.
Our apartment homes are accented with modern, luxury finishes like stainless steel appliances, in-home washer and dryer, and oversized windows.
(Pricing and availability subject to change, plus additional costs for utilities and third-party maintenance services.)
